'''Kharran Fel''' was a large muscly [[human]] [[fighter]]. He was the child of druids from the [[Forgotten Forest]] and although he loved the wilderness, he lacked the inclination to learn to become either a [[ranger]] or a [[druid]]. He did, however, pick up some healing and herbalism skills and also the tracking abilities of a ranger.{{Cite web/The Search for the Circle of Vehlarr/Part One}}
